name: pampas-grass-orange-co-ds35119e1e
notes: This dataset provides the known distribution of pampas grass (Cortaderia selloana) in southern Orange County. The surveys were conducted from May to June, 2007 and were funded by the California Department of Fish and Game. There are four other datasets on invasive plants for this area delineating the distribution of Arundo, Canary Island date palm, Mexican fan palm, and 12 other invasive species.
